WEBVTT

00:04:59.736 --> 00:05:03.400
And while I study the Sun
and its storms every day,

00:05:03.424 --> 00:05:07.350
I will always have a deep love
for this beautiful planet --

00:05:08.076 --> 00:05:09.467
a pale blue dot indeed,

00:05:09.491 --> 00:05:13.375
but a pale blue dot
with an invisible magnetic shield

00:05:13.399 --> 00:05:15.605
that helps to protect us.

00:05:15.629 --> 00:05:16.935
Thank you.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:20.300
(Applause)